### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:3003/tasks

### Pagination
GET http://localhost:3003/tasks?page=1&limit=2

### Filter completed tasks
GET http://localhost:3003/tasks?completed=true

### Sort by createdAt descending
GET http://localhost:3003/tasks?sort=createdAt&order=desc

### Pagination + filter
GET http://localhost:3003/tasks?page=1&limit=2&completed=false

### Create new task
POST http://localhost:3003/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "Build API"
}